Speech Trainer Privacy Policy

This is the Privacy Policy document that is required for all
applications in the Google Play store that request permissions to
record audio.

Speech Trainer application records audio only for the purposes of
playing the audio back to the user. Recorded audio samples are kept in
memory and discarded after the audio is played. Samples are never
written to disk or sent over the network.

Speech Trainer does not track the user in any way.

Speech Trainer does not require any additional permissions other than
the permission to record audio. It does not connect to the Internet,
so it doesn't communicate with advertisement networks or any other
external services.

